13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1354, as
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 66, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
16 Section 1354), is amended to read as follows:
17 Section 1354. There is hereby re-created, to continue until
18 July 1, 2025, pursuant to the provisions of the Oklahoma Sunset Law,
19 the State Board of Examiners of Psychologists. The Board shall
20 administer the provisions of the Psychologists Licensing Act. The
21 Board shall consist of seven (7) members appointed by the Governor.
22 Five members shall be psychologists from various areas in psychology
23 and two members shall be lay persons. At the expiration of the term
24 of each Board member who is a psychologist, the Governor shall
